com.helger.schematron.pure.model

Class PSExtends

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.helger.schematron.pure.model.PSExtends
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPSElement, IPSHasForeignAttributes, Serializable

    @NotThreadSafe
public class PSExtends
extends Object
implements IPSElement, IPSHasForeignAttributes
    A single Schematron extends-element.
    Abstract rules are named lists of assertions without a context expression. The required rule attribute references an abstract rule. The current rule uses all the assertions from the abstract rule it extends.
    Author:
    Philip Helger
